    "title": {
      "rendered": "HOW TO: Easily Accept Stock Donations on Your Nonprofit\u2019s Website \u2013 and Why You Should"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<h5>By <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/kyle-s-brown-ab689481?miniProfileUrn=urn%3Ali%3Afs_miniProfile%3AACoAABFk6ioBTJK5XOAr9A-J57DGwAXKyc7DY6c&amp;lipi=urn%3Ali%3Apage%3Ad_flagship3_search_srp_all%3BKTCvwUNDRw2qBUi%2F92zWTw%3D%3D\">Kyle Brown</a>, COO at <a href=\"https://donatestock.com/\">DonateStock</a> \u2013 a fundraising platform that makes stock gifting to nonprofits easy and accessible.</h5>\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Giving Season is upon us and the clock is ticking. As leadership and development teams lean in for a final push, donors are receiving countless requests for limited financial support.\u00a0</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://donatestock.com\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>DonateStock</strong></span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> has ignited a conversation in philanthropy with its innovative approach to stock gifting. By reducing the friction for donors and nonprofits, stock gifting is now accessible and easy for everyone \u2013 and now donors can donate stock to their favorite cause in just a few clicks.\u00a0</span></p>\n<h2><b>Why Stock Gifting?</b></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Households own $40 trillion in stock. The stock market has created immense wealth for millions of households. Appreciated stock represents the </span><strong><a href=\"https://donatestock.com/why-donate-stock\">most tax-advantaged</a></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> way to support causes donors love for 4 key reasons:\u00a0</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Donors can </span><strong><a href=\"https://donatestock.com/blog/how-to-avoid-capital-gains-tax-on-stocks\">avoid capital gains tax on stocks</a></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> held more than 1 year\u00a0</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Donors can deduct the fair-market value of the gifted stock on tax returns</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nonprofits receive larger pre-tax gifts (vs. after-tax cash gifts)</span></li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https://donatestock.com/for-nonprofits\">Stock gifting is free for donors on DonateStock</a> and offers </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">nonprofits</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> a new way to unlock stock gifting for their organization.\u00a0 </span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2><b>Why Now Is a Good Time to Donate Stock</b></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">More than 50% of US households own stock, with US households over the age of 45 allocating 88% of their assets in investments vs. 12% in cash, according to the 2019 US census. With so much demand on cash, it\u2019s time to offer donors a fresh opportunity at meeting their philanthropic goals by allowing them to donate from their larger holdings of non-cash assets.\u00a0</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Research shows that stock gifting also has a significant impact on nonprofits\u2019 growth and sustainability. Nonprofits that solicit stock gifts grew 5 times faster than those that did not.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://donatestock.com/blog/key-insights-2021-charitable-stock-gifting\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-34387 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-1-e1668779158400.png?resize=800%2C469&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"469\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-1-e1668779158400.png?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-1-e1668779158400.png?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-1-e1668779158400.png?resize=768%2C450&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-1-e1668779158400.png?resize=50%2C29&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a><br />\n<b>Charities that solicit both cash and stock grow 5x faster<br />\nthan those only receiving cash.</b></p>\n<hr />\n<h2><b>How to Sign Up to Accept Stock Donations</b></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Even though stock gifting has been around for decades, it has just now become accessible and easy for all through the online solution, <a href=\"https://donatestock.com/for-nonprofits\">DonateStock</a>.\u00a0</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nonprofits can place their <a href=\"https://donatestock.com/for-nonprofits\">&#8220;Donate Stock&#8221; Easy Button</a> in their Donation form(s) and on their \u201cWays to Give\u201d page. For example, here&#8217;s </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">how World Central Kitchen makes it easy for donors to make a stock gift:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://donatestock.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-34389 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-2-e1668779319311.png?resize=800%2C428&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"428\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-2-e1668779319311.png?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-2-e1668779319311.png?resize=300%2C161&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-2-e1668779319311.png?resize=768%2C411&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-2-e1668779319311.png?resize=50%2C27&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If your nonprofit does not have a stock gifting button, simply visit </span><strong><a href=\"https://donatestock.com/for-nonprofits\">DonateStock</a></strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and search for your nonprofit. If your organization is a 501c3 in good standing, your page already exists and you can claim it by registering at no cost in a matter of minutes:\u00a0</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://donatestock.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-34392 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-3-e1668784260383.png?resize=800%2C640&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"640\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-3-e1668784260383.png?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-3-e1668784260383.png?resize=300%2C240&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-3-e1668784260383.png?resize=768%2C614&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-3-e1668784260383.png?resize=50%2C40&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2>The Stock Gifting Donation Process</h2>\n<p>With Donate Stock, <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">donors can donate stock in just a few clicks; here\u2019s how it works:</span></p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Step #1: Review the Donation Process Overview</b></h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The donor reviews the steps in the donation process and what happens once the gift is initiated.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://donatestock.com/for-nonprofits\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-34394 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-4-e1668785346739.png?resize=800%2C457&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"457\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-4-e1668785346739.png?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-4-e1668785346739.png?resize=300%2C171&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-4-e1668785346739.png?resize=768%2C439&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-4-e1668785346739.png?resize=50%2C29&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Step #2: Enter Brokerage Information</b></h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">New donors enter select brokerage account information in a secure form. They will never be asked for a login username or password, only their brokerage account information. Once entered, it will be saved for future donations.\u00a0 \u00a0</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://donatestock.com/for-nonprofits\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-34396 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-5-e1668785682313.png?resize=800%2C908&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"908\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-5-e1668785682313.png?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-5-e1668785682313.png?resize=264%2C300&amp;ssl=1 264w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-5-e1668785682313.png?resize=768%2C872&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-5-e1668785682313.png?resize=44%2C50&amp;ssl=1 44w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Step #3: Enter Donation Details</b></h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now the fun stuff! The donor enters the ticker symbol(s) and the number of shares they wish to donate, along with the accounting method \u2013 FIFO (first in, first out) is the most common. The platform then calculates the value of the gift based on the current market price.\u00a0</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://donatestock.com/for-nonprofits\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-34401 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-6-e1668785858513.png?resize=800%2C612&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"612\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-6-e1668785858513.png?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-6-e1668785858513.png?resize=300%2C230&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-6-e1668785858513.png?resize=768%2C588&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-6-e1668785858513.png?resize=50%2C38&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Step #4: Review &amp; Confirm Stock Donation</b></h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The donor is asked to review and then confirm their stock gift by providing a digital signature using a trackpad or mouse. After accepting the terms and conditions, the donor clicks &#8220;Submit&#8221; to finalize their stock donation.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://donatestock.com/for-nonprofits\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-34404 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-7-e1668786221314.png?resize=800%2C826&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"826\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-7-e1668786221314.png?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-7-e1668786221314.png?resize=291%2C300&amp;ssl=1 291w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-7-e1668786221314.png?resize=768%2C793&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-7-e1668786221314.png?resize=48%2C50&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Step #5: Stock Donation Confirmation</b></h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Once the donation has been submitted, the order is sent by DonateStock to the donor\u2019s brokerage for execution. Both the donor and nonprofit dashboards are then updated and DonateStock sends each an email to confirm the transaction is in process.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://donatestock.com/for-nonprofits\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-34406 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-8.png?resize=528%2C460&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"528\" height=\"460\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-8.png?w=528&amp;ssl=1 528w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-8.png?resize=300%2C261&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-8.png?resize=50%2C44&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 528px) 100vw, 528px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2>The Donate Stock Nonprofit Dashboard</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It often takes 2-5 business days for the stock to be transferred and received, depending on the time of year.\u00a0</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nonprofits can access their dashboard through their DonateStock account and view donation details:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-9.png?ssl=1\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-34411 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-9-e1668787687993.png?resize=800%2C465&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"465\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-9-e1668787687993.png?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-9-e1668787687993.png?resize=300%2C174&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-9-e1668787687993.png?resize=768%2C446&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Donate-Stock-to-Nonprofits-9-e1668787687993.png?resize=50%2C29&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></p>\n<h2><b>A $100 Billion Opportunity</b></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Appreciated stock represents $100 billion in potential funding. By making stock gifting accessible and easy for all, stock is poised to become a major source of funding for nonprofits of all sizes.\u00a0</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To learn more about stock gifting and other resources available for nonprofits and donors, </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">check out the <a href=\"https://donatestock.com/blog\">DonateStock blog</a></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, d</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ownload </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">the </span><a href=\"https://donatestock.com/blog/download-the-ultimate-stock-gifting-guide-for-nonprofits\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Ultimate</strong> <strong>Stock Gifting Guide for Nonprofits</strong></span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, and watch the <a href=\"https://vimeo.com/756918736/5fbdebf7b1\">DonateStock Donor Experience for Nonprofits video</a>.\u00a0</span></p>\n<div style=\"background-color: #8362ae; padding: 4px;\"></div>\n<div style=\"background-color: #efebeb; padding: 5px;\">\n<h2><strong> \u25ba </strong><b>About the Sponsor</b></h2>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background-color: #efebeb; padding: 5px; text-align: left;\"><a style=\"color: #8362ae;\" href=\"https://donatestock.com/\">DonateStock</a>\u00a0<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">is transforming charitable giving by making stock gifting easy and accessible for all donors and nonprofits. With a stock gifting Easy Button it is easy for nonprofits to solicit and accept stock donations at scale. When supporters donate stock, they can avoid capital gains tax on stock gifts while deducting the current value of the stock donation\u2014resulting in substantial tax savings for them and larger pre-tax gifts for your nonprofit. When donors gift stock, everyone wins.</span></div>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://donatestock.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-32184\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DonateStock.com_.jpg?resize=800%2C399&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"399\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DonateStock.com_.jpg?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DonateStock.com_.jpg?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DonateStock.com_.jpg?resize=768%2C383&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DonateStock.com_.jpg?resize=50%2C25&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n",
