      "rendered": "<p>Stock gifting has a significant impact on nonprofits\u2019 growth and sustainability. In fact, nonprofits that solicit stock gifts grow 5X faster than those that do not \u2013 and even though stock gifting has been around for decades, it has only recently become accessible and easy to donate online using DonateStock.com. </p>\n",
